data.text: @anattack001 Ya know what I'm saying??? I know they're hungry and times are tough, but c'mon
@Potszicle Thank youuuuu!!!! When is this bish gonna start showing but a bump? It’s been like a year since Glenn died!!!

@anattack001 It's unrealistic, even for a zombie apocalypse, for all this nonsense to go on. There's no development, just the occasional zombie, a pissing contest between Rick and Negan, and Maggie isn't even pregnant haha

@Potszicle It really has. We’ve supported every season, every episode, every boring ass character, but this is too much. I have no idea what is happening, everything seems spun together poorly and Negan, Rick and the gang have been a let down. I’m like WTF guys.
@anattack001 Ayyyyyy, so true. We've had the same episode the last 4 episodes. This whole season sucked so far.

@Potszicle Ayyyyyy im over TWD. This show is killing me. It’s so boring anymore and nothing is happening and Negan ain’t shit. We literally watch it a couple days later on the DVR. We’re so over it but have given 7 years so we have to see it through.
@anattack001 That or TWD, sadly. And she really is. Nude and sinister, what more do you need. She's a present day Lady MacBeth
@Potszicle GoT is never going to get proper recognition, especially Heady who is the best character in that show.

@anattack001 Wow - I'm pleasantly surprised! The only thing I'm displeased about is Michelle Pfeiffer and Lena Heady being robbed nominations for mother! and GOT.  I'm glad Call Me By Your Name is getting recognized, and Jessica Chastain for Molly's Game!!!
